<section id="for-evaluators">
    <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">For Talent Evaluators</h2>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-md mb-6">
        <p class="mb-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">I've built this MCP server to help a wide range of people evaluate whether I might be a good fit for their needs:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Recruiters:</strong> Ask about my experience, skills, and background directly.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Hiring managers:</strong> Drill into my proficiency in specific technologies. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "What's Jake's proficiency level with React, TypeScript, and AWS?"</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Interview coordinators:</strong> Generate tailored phone screens and take-home questions. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Create a phone screen for Jake around API design and testing."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Clients & product owners:</strong> Summarize my past projects, tech stack, and potential ROI. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Summarize Jake's experience building scalable microservices."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Conference organizers:</strong> Vet topics, domain expertise, or draft talks and bios. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Draft a talk abstract for Jake on serverless architectures."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Mentors & peers:</strong> Fetch code samples, contributions, or blog posts. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "List Jake's top GitHub contributions in the last year."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Career coaches:</strong> Pull my resume, GitHub stats, and website content for assessments. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Generate a summary of Jake's career highlights."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Automated HR tools:</strong> Integrate my profile into scoring workflows or dashboards. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Compare Jake's skill set vs other applicants for the frontend role."</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Anyone evaluating my fit:</strong> Use the prompt: <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">"Is Jake a good fit for my role? [paste job description]"</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Product managers & designers:</strong> Understand how I collaborate on product vision and feature prioritization. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "How would Jake contribute to our feature roadmap development?"</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Learning & development teams:</strong> Discover topics I can teach or workshops I could lead. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "What workshop could Jake deliver on TypeScript best practices?"</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Diversity & inclusion leaders:</strong> Explore how my background aligns with D&I goals. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "How can Jake support our organization's diversity initiatives?"</span></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Startup founders & small teams:</strong> Assess my fit as a generalist in lean environments. <span class="italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: "Would Jake be a good fit for a full-stack generalist role at an early-stage startup?"</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900 dark:bg-opacity-30 rounded border-l-4 border-blue-500">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">ðŸ’¡ <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Pro Tip:</strong> Connect your AI assistant to this MCP server using the instructions above, then have it analyze my experience against your specific requirements to streamline your evaluation process.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Get a Complete Candidate Assessment</h3>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-md mb-4">
        <p class="mb-3 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Once connected, your AI assistant can provide a thorough evaluation of my candidacy:</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
            {% import "partials/assessment-card.njk" as ac %}
            
            {{ ac.assessment_card(
                title="Skills Assessment",
                description="Ask about specific technologies or skills mentioned in your job description and get an analysis of my experience level with each.",
                example="What is Jake's proficiency level with React, TypeScript, and AWS?"
            ) }}
            
            {{ ac.assessment_card(
                title="Business Impact",
                description="Understand how my background could translate to impact in your organization based on my previous roles and accomplishments.",
                example="How could Jake contribute to our e-commerce platform optimization efforts?"
            ) }}
            
            {{ ac.assessment_card(
                title="Strengths & Growth Areas",
                description="Get insights into which aspects of your role I would likely excel at, and where I might need support or development.",
                example="Based on our senior developer role, what are Jake's strengths and potential growth areas?"
            ) }}
            
            {{ ac.assessment_card(
                title="Phone Screen Generator",
                description="Generate customized interview questions that focus on the specific unknowns or areas you want to explore further.",
                example="Create a phone screen for Jake focused on system design and leadership skills."
            ) }}
        </div>
    </div>

    {% import "partials/feature-card.njk" as fc %}
    
    {% call fc.feature_card(
        title="Take Action",
        description="If you're using the hosted version at <code>ai.jakegaylor.com/mcp</code>, you can have your AI assistant contact me directly:",
        has_margin_bottom=false
    ) %}
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">The assistant can compose an email based on your role and my qualifications, which you can review and send. This helps create a personalized outreach that highlights the specific reasons why your opportunity might align with my background.</p>
        <p class="text-xs italic text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Example: Ask your assistant: "Please draft an email to Jake about our [position name] role and why he might be a good fit."</p>
    {% endcall %}
    
    {{ fc.feature_card(
        title="Technical Deep Dive", 
        description="Walk through core technologies in your stack, explore my project work via the GitHub MCP server, and discuss design trade-offs:", 
        example="Give me a code walk-through of Jake's use of AWS Lambda in his last project and ask him to explain the trade-offs."
    ) }}
    
    {{ fc.feature_card(
        title="Onboarding & Ramp Roadmap", 
        description="Generate a 30-60-90-day plan based on my background and your team's goals:", 
        example="Create a 90-day onboarding roadmap for Jake joining as a senior platform engineer."
    ) }}
    
    {{ fc.feature_card(
        title="Growth & Development Plan", 
        description="Identify skill gaps and suggest learning paths or stretch projects:", 
        example="What areas should Jake focus on to become our next team lead, and what projects could we assign him?"
    ) }}
    
    {{ fc.feature_card(
        title="Reference Simulation", 
        description="Auto-generate reference-check questions or simulate testimonial responses:", 
        example="Create three reference-check questions about Jake's leadership and history of delivering results."
    ) }}
</section> 